subproject.description: The main thrust of this project is to provide consolidated UN support to the evolution of national development plans and processes. Also, it is to provide substantive inputs to development initiatives in the country. This support is articulated through strengthening delivering as one, joint/common programming, support to gender mainstreaming, rights-based approach, and HIV/AID, support in simplifying and harmonizing such common services as HACT, travel, health etc
subproject.gender code: Gender equality as a significant objective
subproject.title: RC - Coordination for Results
